<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> I'll admit they're kinda rare, but saying 1% is just foolish, seeing as at least ONE always dropped on EVERY neh/rak raid Ive been on - Montyy<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
