<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> Reavers aren't camped 24/7 so any druid/ranger CAN attempt to kill them, whereas Sev IS caped 24/7 so its harder for a war or pally to kill him. - Montyy<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
You are saying that 100*1 is bigger than 10*10 because 100 is bigger than 10. The spawn rate or the drop rate alone are not significant. The product of the two is what is important. How many come into the world in any time frame is what is important.<br>
<br>
This determines <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> supply</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END-->.<br>
<br>
How how desired they are is determined by relative obsolesence of the epic and the number of people that need it. For Warriors obsolescence is relatively high and number of people wanting it is relatively low. For Druids/Ranger obsolescence is low and number of people wanting it is high (two classes, one of which is the most popular in the game).<br>
<br>
This determines <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> demand</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END-->.<br>
<br>
Those two together determine value, which is dynamic.<br>
<br>
As for Green Scales specifically, before MB was nerfed, it was actually much easier for a Warrior to get a green scale than a druid/ranger to get a reaver. All he had to do was camp there until Sev popped. He could get his guild.. if they were available.. or get burners if not. Guilds and burners would always come because of the secondary loots (to the warrior) and the minimal time they must expend to get them. The warrior did the waiting alone. Even now the warrior can still camp it and get his guild, or, if not have an ok shot at putting together a pickup raid. This requires some knowlege of organizing a raid.. but it's not that hard to do, and not that hard to find people to kill dragons. The main risk is someone you ask getting their own people and ganking it.<br>
<br>
And you are dreaming. Sev is almost NEVER camped except right after a patch. And not always even then. That's the reality. VoR camps him sometimes. Lonin camped him. A couple of others.<br>
<br>
Constrast this with a rng/dru getting people to go to CoM. It's damned hard. XP sucks. Loot sucks. It takes a LOT of time. You get tired of asking and feel guilty.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> Black Reaver's = possibly 1000 in the same amount of time that Sev takes to spawn. - Zeik<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
