<br>
Nor have I said that jade reaver drops are rare because people can't get a group together to kill them.  What you're twisting out of context is that I've said that it's unrealistic to think a group is going to stay in City of Mist around the clock until a jade reaver drops.<br>
I have also said that what's trivial to group of twinks and access to spells above their average group level is not necessarily going to be trivial to a full group of people with lower quality gear.  <br>
<br>
You're sounding like a broken record.<br>
